@api_url = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = 

### Create UserAnswer (Newcomer form submission)
POST {{api_url}}/user-answers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Martin",
  "birthdate": "1998-04-22",
  "codePostal": "33000",
  "phoneNumber": "0612345678",
  "email": "alice.martin@example.com",
  "collecteId": 1,
  "slotIds": [1, 2],
  "zoneIds": [1]
}

### Create UserAnswer with existing user
POST {{api_url}}/user-answers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Bob",
  "lastName": "Dupont",
  "birthdate": "1992-01-10",
  "codePostal": "13001",
  "phoneNumber": "0612345678",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "collecteId": 1,
  "slotIds": [3],
  "zoneIds": [1, 2]
}

### Update UserAnswer (change one slot/zone and profile)
PUT {{api_url}}/user-answers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Martin",
  "birthdate": "1998-04-22",
  "codePostal": "33100",
  "phoneNumber": "0612345678",
  "email": "alice.martin@example.com",
  "slotId": 2,
  "zoneId": 1
}

### Get UserAnswer by ID
GET {{api_url}}/user-answers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all UserAnswers for a Collection
GET {{api_url}}/collections/1/user-answers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete UserAnswer
DELETE {{api_url}}/user-answers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
